file.name: resources.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  version: 0.0.1
  title: '@viron/example-nodejs resources'
  description: resources api specifications

tags:
  - name: resource

paths:
  /resources/{resourceName}/downloads:
    get:
      operationId: downloadResources
      tags:
        - resource
      summary: download resources
      description: データダウンロード
      parameters:
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/ResourceNamePathParam'
        - $ref: '#/components/parameters/FormatQueryParam'
      responses:
        200:
          description: OK
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: string
            text/csv:
              schema:
                type: string
      security:
        - jwt: []

components:
  parameters:
    ResourceNamePathParam:
      name: resourceName
      in: path
      schema:
        type: string
      required: true

    FormatQueryParam:
      name: format
      in: query
      schema:
        type: string
        enum:
          - json
          - csv
        default: json
      required: false
